Package: tidycreel
Title: Tidy Interface for Creel Survey Design and Analysis
Version: 1.1.0
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Christopher", family = "Chizinski", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "chris.chizinski@unl.edu",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9294-2588"))
Description: Provides a tidy, pipe-friendly interface for creel survey
    design, data management, estimation, and reporting. Built on the 'survey'
    package for robust design-based inference with support for access-point,
    roving, and hybrid survey designs.
